<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:98px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Sabotaging someone&rsquo;s work on purpose.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Engaging in frequent or unwanted advances of any nature.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Commenting derogatorily on a person&rsquo;s ethnic heritage or religious beliefs.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Starting or spreading rumors about a person&rsquo;s personal life.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Ridiculing someone in front of others or singling them out to perform tasks unrelated to their job (e.g. bringing coffee) against their will.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<div style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'>
    <ol start="1" style="margin-bottom:0cm;list-style-type: lower-alpha;margin-left:62px;">
        <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><span style="font-size:16px;">Sexual harassment is illegal and we will seriously investigate relevant reports. If an employee or client is found guilty of sexual harassment, they will be terminated &amp; prosecuted under Indian laws.&nbsp;</span></li>
    </ol>
</div>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">Our sexual harassment policy aims to protect men and women in our company from unwanted sexual advances and give them guidelines to report incidents. We won&rsquo;t tolerate sexual harassment in our workplace in any shape or form. Our culture is based on mutual respect and collaboration. Sexual harassment is a serious violation of those principles.</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">1a. Sexual harassment has many forms of variable seriousness. A person sexually harasses someone when they:</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:98px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Insinuate, propose or demand sexual favors of any kind.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Invade another person&rsquo;s personal space (e.g. inappropriate touching.)</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Stalk, intimidate, coerce or threaten another person to get them to engage in sexual acts.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Send or display sexually explicit objects or messages.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Comment on someone&rsquo;s looks, dress, sexuality, or gender in a derogatory or objectifying manner or a manner that makes them uncomfortable.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Make obscene comments, jokes, or gestures that humiliate or offend someone.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Pursue or flirt with another person persistently without the other person&rsquo;s willing participation. Also, flirting with someone at an inappropriate time (e.g. in a team meeting) is considered sexual harassment, even when these advances would have been welcome in a different setting. This is because such actions can harm a person&rsquo;s professional reputation and expose them to further harassment.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">The most extreme form of sexual harassment is sexual assault. This is a serious crime and our company will support a victim who wants to press charges against offenders.</span></li>
</ul>



<div style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'>
    <ol style="margin-bottom:0cm;list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:53px;">
        <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">PRIVACY</span></strong></li>
    </ol>
</div>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:63.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">Usage of services is also governed by the privacy policy available at {</span><a href="http://www.hireforcare.com"><span style="font-size:16px;color:windowtext;background:white;">www.hireforcare.com</span></a><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">}</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:12.0pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<div style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'>
    <ol style="margin-bottom:0cm;list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:53px;">
        <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:115%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">Employment Contract</span></strong></li>
    </ol>
</div>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:63.0pt;text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<ol style="list-style-type: decimal;margin-left:62px;">
    <li><strong><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">Scope of Work</span></strong></li>
</ol>
<ul style="list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:98px;">
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">The company shall intimate the helper the details of the client for whom the helper needs to go and work.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">The helper shall have the right to refuse to work for a particular client for genuine reasons explained to the company and accepted by the company.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">If required by the company, the helper will be on trial for 30 days or a such number of days as may be determined by the company (<strong>&ldquo;Trial Period&rdquo;)&nbsp;</strong>during which the company may choose to send the helper to work for a client or train/keep the helper in-house. The company may choose to not associate itself with the helper if the services of the helper are found unsatisfactory by the company, whether directly or indirectly.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">The company will be entitled to conduct verification of helpers credentials as may deem fit by the company and the helper shall cooperate with the company completely in this regard. The company, in its sole discretion, is not bound to provide any notice to the helper prior to or post conducting the aforesaid verification checks. The company and/or the client is also entitled to conduct a medical examination of the helper and the helper shall cooperate with the company. Client completely in this regard.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">Any communication that the helper wishes to have regarding the conduct/treatment of the client shall be direct with the company. The helper shall consult the company in case of any concerns/issues during the course of employment which shall include the period for which the helper is acting as domestic help of the client.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">The helper will be entitled for 2 leaves in a month, If the helper avails leaves beyond this period, then the company will be entitled to deduct the salary of the helper.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">The helper shall in no circumstance, agree to work on an independent basis for the lenient or any other person associated with/recommended by the client or any their party till the time the helper is associated with the company.&nbsp;</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">The helper shall not work with/for the client or any person associated with/recommended by the client for a period of <strong>3 months</strong> after leaving the employment of the company.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:108.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">12. Retention</span></strong></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:98px;">
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">In case a client does not want to continue with the helper&rsquo;s tenure &amp; the helper has been rated good by the client, then the helper <strong>can get an option to get a part of their last drawn salary as per the calculations defined by the company</strong></span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">This is applicable only for basic helper performance while working for a minimum tenure of 90 days.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">The company can terminate the contract by updating the helper on the termination of the contract &amp; bound to pay the required amount till that day by the 10th of the consecutive month. If helper joins somewhere/started working (not suggested by hireforcare private limited) during idle time then hireforcare private limited is not bound to pay anything to the helper</span></li>
</ul>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">13. <strong>Payment Policy</strong></span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:36.0pt;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ol start="1" style="list-style-type: lower-alpha;margin-left:98px;">
    <li><span style="line-height:115%;background:white;">Only Direct Payment to Hireforcare: You don&apos;t have to pay the caregiver in cash or cheque unless asked by the Hireforcare Customer Service team. You will be paying Hireforcare directly Online/App or request a cash/cheque pickup.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:115%;background:white;">Payment Mode: App, Online, NEFT, Cheque, and Cash payments are accepted. Hireforcare promotes and prefers online payment in advance which enables us to pay our caregivers in time without hassle. For Cash/Cheque pickup amount should be more than Rs. 2000/- any amount below it should be paid online.</span></li>
    <li><strong><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">Change in Fees</span></strong><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;background:white;">. We may change the existing Fees or make new additions to the existing fees upon thirty (30) days&apos; earlier composed notice to the User &amp; Helper. Despite the previous, we may expand the Fees, quickly and with parallel notice, in case of (an) any adjustment in the administrations or expenses of our outsider specialist co-ops; (b) changes in the Services which are made at your demand; or (c) delays and additionally different issues because of User &amp; Helper inability to satisfy User &amp; Helper commitments or because of User &amp; Helper ask for to defer work under any circumstances.&nbsp;</span></li>
</ol>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:63.0pt;text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;14. &nbsp;Employment Terms</span></strong></p>
<ol start="1" style="margin-bottom:0cm;margin-top:0cm;" type="1">
    <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">The helper <strong>acknowledges and understands</strong> that the client has the right to check the bags/purse or any other belonging of the helper which the helper is carrying to &nbsp;the client&rsquo;s premises. The helper shall not resist the same and shall cooperate with the client in this regard.</span></li>
    <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">The helper shall be truthful and honest during his/her tenor with the company including while providing the services to the client and shall not indulge in any criminal activity. Any criminal activity on the helper&rsquo;s part shall entitle the company and /or the client to take severe action against the helper including filing a police complaint.</span></li>
    <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">In the event, the helper causes any damage to the company/clients belongings and/or premises or any other premise where the helper is placed by the company or breaks anything or renders anything unusable during the trial period or during her tenure with the client or during the term the helper is associated with the company, the company shall be entitled to deduct a suitable amount from the helper&rsquo;s salary to recover for the loss of any or If there is no pending salary, then Helper should bear required amount to reimburse the damage and company/client has right to take legal action.</span></li>
    <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">In the event the helper stops coming to work for the client without prior notice of <strong>30</strong> <strong>days</strong> to the client and the company, then the company shall not be bound to pay for the number of days the helper has served the client. In addition, the company shall be entitled to remove the helper from its services on an immediate basis.</span></li>
    <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">The helper shall in no circumstance, agree to work on an independent basis for the lenient or any other person associated with/recommended by the client or any their party till the time the helper is associated with the company. The helper shall not work with/for the client or any person associated with/recommended by the client for a period of <strong>3 months</strong> after leaving the employment of the company.]</span></li>
    <li style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;">In the events of termination, a lapse in tenure, exiting from the company, and any other financial dues &amp; clearance will be evaluated by the company following with any type of reimbursement and dues will be processed on the 5th of every consecutive month.</span></li>
</ol>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:36.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;background:white;">15. Harassment Policy&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">Our anti-harassment policy expresses our commitment to maintaining a workplace that&rsquo;s free of harassment, so our employees/helpers can feel safe and happy. We will not tolerate anyone intimidating, humiliating, or sabotaging others during work. We also prohibit willful discrimination based on [age, sexual orientation, ethnicity, race, religion, or disability.]. This harassment policy applies to all hireforcare employees, clients, helpers, public visitors, customers, and anyone else whom helpers come into contact with at work.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">Harassment includes bullying, intimidation, direct insults, malicious gossip, and victimization. We can&rsquo;t create an exhaustive list, but here are some instances that we consider harassment:</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:98px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Sabotaging someone&rsquo;s work on purpose.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Engaging in frequent or unwanted advances of any nature.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Commenting derogatorily on a person&rsquo;s ethnic heritage or religious beliefs.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Starting or spreading rumors about a person&rsquo;s personal life.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Ridiculing someone in front of others or singling them out to perform tasks unrelated to their job (e.g. bringing coffee) against their will.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">Sexual harassment is illegal and we will seriously investigate relevant reports. If an employee or client is found guilty of sexual harassment, they will be terminated &amp; prosecuted under Indian laws.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">Our sexual harassment policy aims to protect men and women in our company from unwanted sexual advances and give them guidelines to report incidents. We won&rsquo;t tolerate sexual harassment at our workplace and client space in any shape or form. Our culture is based on mutual respect and collaboration. Sexual harassment is a serious violation of those principles.</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">a. Sexual harassment has many forms of variable seriousness. A person sexually harasses someone when they:</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";margin-left:72.0pt;text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:98px;">
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Insinuate, propose or demand sexual favors of any kind.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Invade another person&rsquo;s personal space (e.g. inappropriate touching.)</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Stalk, intimidate, coerce or threaten another person to get them to engage in sexual acts.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Send or display sexually explicit objects or messages.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Comment on someone&rsquo;s looks, dress, sexuality, or gender in a derogatory or objectifying manner or a manner that makes them uncomfortable.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Make obscene comments, jokes, or gestures that humiliate or offend someone.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">Pursue or flirt with another person persistently without the other person&rsquo;s willing participation. Also, flirting with someone at an inappropriate time is considered sexual harassment, even when these advances would have been welcome in a different setting. This is because such actions can harm a person&rsquo;s professional reputation and expose them to further harassment.</span></li>
    <li><span style="font-size:16px;">The most extreme form of sexual harassment is sexual assault. This is a serious crime and our company will support a victim who wants to press charges against offenders.</span></li>
</ul>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">You agree and acknowledge that we shall have the right to:</span></strong></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<ul style="list-style-type: undefined;margin-left:26px;">
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">Share the information provided by you with users who can contact you for your job requirements</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">Use the information provided by you for the purpose of gathering market intelligence including but not limited to customer surveys, analysis of customer data, customer data, marketing, press releases, etc.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">Use your contact address/details may be used to provide information to you about Website marketing activities, new deals, renewal reminders, payment reminders, reviews, which opinion, which would not be deemed unsolicited correspondence.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">Share Personal Information if We believe it is necessary in order to investigate, prevent, or take action regarding illegal activities, suspected fraud, situations involving potential threats to the physical safety of any person, violations of various terms and conditions, or our policies.</span></li>
    <li><span style="line-height:107%;background:white;font-size:16px;background:white;">Disclose any information (including the identity of the persons providing information or materials on the Websites) as necessary to satisfy any law, regulation, or valid governmental request, including information in connection with an investigation of alleged illegal activity or solicitation of illegal activity to law enforcement or other government officials or in response to a lawful court order</span></li>
</ul>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Arial","sans-serif";text-align:justify;'><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;background:white;">&nbsp;</span></p>
